WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:58.000 --> 02:01.527
Stop!

02:10.479 --> 02:14.201
Mister, you got some money for us?

02:14.560 --> 02:16.085
Come on.

02:17.720 --> 02:19.051
Quick.

02:21.640 --> 02:23.130
Quick!

05:27.760 --> 05:32.322
WUJINSHAN (Black Gold Mountain)

05:56.200 --> 05:58.202
Which way to Wujinshan?

05:58.280 --> 05:59.361
You're here.

05:59.440 --> 06:02.683
- Highway 307?
- This is it.

07:31.000 --> 07:32.161
Dahai.

07:54.440 --> 07:56.169
Whose trike is that outside?

07:56.240 --> 07:57.969
I don't know.

07:58.080 --> 07:59.445
No?

08:01.600 --> 08:03.489
Sit down, Dahai.

08:03.560 --> 08:07.281
It's been there two days.
No idea whose it is.

08:07.360 --> 08:10.250
If no one wants it, I'll sell it.

08:13.080 --> 08:16.687
So if the village chief's Audi
A6 sat outside his house,

08:16.760 --> 08:18.888
you'd sell that too?

08:18.960 --> 08:20.041
What do you think?

08:20.120 --> 08:23.408
His A6 belongs to
everyone in the village.

08:23.520 --> 08:27.241
He sold the state-owned coal
mine so he could afford it.

08:27.360 --> 08:29.840
No wonder the car
looks so familiar.

08:29.920 --> 08:32.764
Those shiny wheels
are actually mine.

08:32.840 --> 08:35.081
You're smart.

08:35.200 --> 08:36.645
Dahai.

08:36.720 --> 08:38.847
A pity you weren't born earlier.

08:38.919 --> 08:40.967
In the war years,

08:41.080 --> 08:44.208
you'd surely have made general.

08:44.280 --> 08:45.725
Just see what happens.

08:45.800 --> 08:48.167
When I report to Beijing,

08:48.240 --> 08:52.245
the chief and the new boss Jiao
will be hauling sand in prison.

08:52.320 --> 08:56.609
Before you even get to Taiyuan,
the chief's men will catch you.

08:56.720 --> 08:59.724
Why do you think I studied law?

08:59.800 --> 09:03.088
The chief sold off
collectively owned property.

09:03.160 --> 09:05.208
He accepted a bribe.

09:05.280 --> 09:07.248
That'll get him 20 years.

09:07.320 --> 09:11.041
As for your boss Jiao Shengli,
he's rolling in it, right?

09:11.120 --> 09:14.681
I'll accuse him of polluting and
covering up accidents in the mine.

09:14.760 --> 09:16.364
They'll close him down.

09:16.440 --> 09:18.841
Believe it.

09:19.840 --> 09:25.688
If the coal mine had gone to you,
you'd have been no different.

09:25.760 --> 09:27.649
I would have.

09:27.720 --> 09:32.328
Jiao's Maserati is parked in
the yard. Nobody uses it.

09:32.400 --> 09:35.768
Drive it off and sell it. Then
you can buy us all a drink.

09:35.840 --> 09:38.161
I don't want his fucking car.

09:41.200 --> 09:44.761
- Sanming. Got the train ticket?
- Yes.

09:44.840 --> 09:48.003
- Where are you going?
- To see my wife for New Year's.

09:48.080 --> 09:50.162
That's romantic.

09:51.240 --> 09:53.242
The police are here.

09:53.360 --> 09:55.169
Stop eating.

09:57.760 --> 09:59.603
Investigation.

09:59.680 --> 10:02.286
Are all the migrant workers here?

10:02.360 --> 10:03.691
Yes. What's wrong?

10:03.760 --> 10:07.128
A murder in Shibawan. The
migrants have to be checked.

10:07.200 --> 10:10.283
Get them all outside.

10:10.360 --> 10:12.089
Hurry!

10:19.120 --> 10:20.406
Chief.

10:20.480 --> 10:21.641
Village Chief.

10:21.720 --> 10:25.770
When you sold off the coal mine
you promised yearly dividends.

10:25.840 --> 10:27.808
I said that in private.

10:27.880 --> 10:29.723
I don't have time now.

10:29.800 --> 10:33.168
Okay, explain it to the
Discipline Commission.

10:37.720 --> 10:41.725
You've picked the wrong
time for a fight.

10:42.640 --> 10:45.450
You'll be a loser your whole life.

10:58.000 --> 11:01.607
- You won't discuss it?
- You talk too much.

11:10.600 --> 11:14.127
Okay. People from Chongqing.

11:32.560 --> 11:33.766
Over there.

11:33.840 --> 11:35.126
Next.

11:56.480 --> 11:58.369
He's making a run for it!

12:19.360 --> 12:20.885
Damn animal!

13:08.120 --> 13:09.167
What's up, Dahai?

13:09.240 --> 13:12.084
I'm writing to the
Discipline Commission

13:12.160 --> 13:15.289
to complain about the
chief and Jiao Shengli.

13:16.200 --> 13:18.726
Miss, a registered letter.

13:18.800 --> 13:22.691
- To whom?
- Beijing. Zhongnanhai. The Commission.

13:22.760 --> 13:25.491
I need the full address.

13:25.560 --> 13:27.403
Zhongnanhai, Beijing.

13:27.480 --> 13:30.689
That's not enough.
I need the full address.

13:30.760 --> 13:34.082
What? Everyone knows Zhongnanhai.

13:34.160 --> 13:36.162
That's not enough.

13:36.240 --> 13:39.130
Miss, are you siding
with the village chief?

13:39.200 --> 13:41.521
Does he give you kickbacks?

13:41.600 --> 13:45.605
Or are you Jiao's mistress?
Has he bought you a car?

13:45.680 --> 13:47.762
You're crazy! Go away!

13:48.520 --> 13:51.000
You two must be in league.

13:51.080 --> 13:52.969
There's no justice!

13:53.040 --> 13:54.280
No justice!

13:54.960 --> 13:56.689
No justice.

14:07.280 --> 14:11.205
All aboard! We're leaving, hurry!

14:11.280 --> 14:14.124
Dahai, come on!

14:15.560 --> 14:16.641
What's this for?

14:16.720 --> 14:20.805
Greeting Boss Jiao. One
bag of flour per person.

14:26.560 --> 14:30.485
Boss Jiao has a new private plane.
He's flying back from Hong Kong.

14:30.560 --> 14:33.928
We're a welcoming group.
Everyone gets a bag of flour.

14:34.000 --> 14:37.368
A plane? Living on this
earth isn't enough?

14:41.960 --> 14:44.725
Were you at the coal mine
when the gun was fired?

14:44.800 --> 14:46.370
Yes.

14:47.160 --> 14:49.322
Who was the guy who ran away?

14:49.400 --> 14:52.927
A loader in the coal yard.
From Sichuan.

14:53.000 --> 14:56.686
Why did he run?
The killings in Shibawan?

14:56.760 --> 14:58.922
He's an escaped prisoner.

14:59.040 --> 15:02.169
Killed someone in his hometown.
He's been hiding here.

15:02.240 --> 15:04.083
He thought they'd come for him.

15:04.160 --> 15:06.561
He panicked and ran.

15:06.640 --> 15:10.122
- Did they catch him?
- Of course.

15:13.320 --> 15:16.210
- What happened in Shibawan?
- Don't you know?

15:16.280 --> 15:20.968
Someone shot three guys yesterday.
Three dead in Shibawan.

15:21.040 --> 15:23.611
- Who did it?
- I don't know.

15:23.680 --> 15:28.527
Early this morning, a bunch of
armed police were in Shibawan.

15:29.360 --> 15:31.522
I see.

15:34.760 --> 15:38.367
Accountant Liu, are your
accounts up to date?

15:40.120 --> 15:44.170
When Boss Jiao got
hold of the coal mine

15:44.240 --> 15:47.722
he said 40% of the profits
would go to the village.

15:47.840 --> 15:52.402
How much do the last 14
years' dividends come to?

15:52.480 --> 15:55.529
Listen, back in 2001,

15:55.640 --> 15:59.167
the village committee signed
to sell the coal mine.

15:59.240 --> 16:01.242
Who asked you to sell it?

16:01.320 --> 16:03.607
Was the contract discussed?

16:03.680 --> 16:05.921
We must keep our word.

16:06.000 --> 16:10.961
But Jiao got so rich he
even bought a plane.

16:11.040 --> 16:13.088
He's a hard worker.

16:13.200 --> 16:19.321
Then tell me how much you and
the chief took in bribes.

16:19.400 --> 16:21.562
Stop, please.

16:23.240 --> 16:26.164
Tell me how much you
took in bribes.

16:26.240 --> 16:27.765
Open the door.

16:27.880 --> 16:32.522
Devils like you are more evil
than the village chief and Jiao.

16:38.920 --> 16:42.606
- Listen to me...
- Don't talk to me.

16:51.280 --> 16:54.170
Everyone, repeat after me.

16:54.600 --> 16:55.681
Welcome! Welcome!

16:55.760 --> 16:57.330
A warm welcome!

17:00.640 --> 17:02.085
Good.

17:03.240 --> 17:05.208
Here's the plane!

18:02.680 --> 18:05.763
Mr. Jiao, you've
reached a new level.

18:05.840 --> 18:08.525
Let's progress together.

18:08.600 --> 18:10.841
Congratulations, ma'am.

18:10.920 --> 18:12.684
Kids, the flowers.

18:21.800 --> 18:24.087
Mr. Jiao, look this way.

18:26.680 --> 18:29.126
A bit closer, please.

18:30.040 --> 18:33.362
- Please say something, sir.
- Later.

18:45.040 --> 18:47.042
How are you, Auntie?

18:51.000 --> 18:52.809
Thanks for coming.

18:52.880 --> 18:54.803
Long time no see.

18:54.880 --> 18:57.486
- Shengli!
- Dahai.

18:57.560 --> 18:59.642
Congratulations.

18:59.720 --> 19:01.643
Thank you, Dahai.

19:01.720 --> 19:03.848
You're a hard man to reach.

19:03.920 --> 19:05.968
There's something
I want to discuss.

19:06.080 --> 19:08.048
Can you do me a favor?

19:08.120 --> 19:10.043
Whatever you need, just ask.

19:10.120 --> 19:11.963
Sponsor my journey to Beijing

19:12.040 --> 19:15.442
to file accusations against
you and the village chief.

19:15.960 --> 19:18.770
Sure, come and pick it up later.

19:18.840 --> 19:21.207
Here, in front of all
these villagers,

19:21.280 --> 19:24.443
can't you discuss the
village economy?

19:28.120 --> 19:30.407
What are you staring at?

20:09.440 --> 20:12.683
Xiao Bai, are you playing golf?

20:44.680 --> 20:48.480
I'm here to compensate you on
behalf of the Shengli Group.

21:08.680 --> 21:10.523
Case closed.

22:51.480 --> 22:53.209
Where's your mother?

22:53.280 --> 22:56.887
- Who are you?
- Don't you remember me?

22:56.960 --> 23:00.726
I'm your uncle from Wujinshan.

23:00.800 --> 23:04.202
Mom went out for food.
She'll be back soon.

23:09.640 --> 23:12.325
Animal.

23:15.400 --> 23:17.368
Where's your dad?

23:17.440 --> 23:20.683
Out hunting "animals."

23:20.760 --> 23:22.842
On which mountain?

23:22.960 --> 23:24.644
Jiaokou.

23:26.880 --> 23:28.609
Dahai.

23:29.320 --> 23:30.651
You've...

23:32.160 --> 23:34.322
When did you get here?

23:34.400 --> 23:37.085
I've been in town a couple of days.

23:37.720 --> 23:39.688
Let's go inside.

23:40.200 --> 23:42.885
Ganggang. Eat first, then homework.

23:42.960 --> 23:44.962
Of course, Mom.

23:45.920 --> 23:47.809
You're...

23:49.720 --> 23:51.370
Tell me.

23:55.440 --> 23:59.161
A while back, I introduced
you to a woman from Wangcun.

23:59.240 --> 24:01.288
You were well matched.

24:01.360 --> 24:02.566
But you...

24:02.640 --> 24:05.723
Why didn't you date
her, as arranged?

24:05.800 --> 24:09.930
You never think about your life.

24:12.720 --> 24:15.087
All you do is make accusations.

24:15.160 --> 24:18.846
Even if your charges
stick, you'll grow old.

24:18.920 --> 24:22.766
I'm already old. But I don't care.

24:22.840 --> 24:24.649
Don't be silly.

24:24.720 --> 24:27.405
You're only middle-aged.

24:32.560 --> 24:34.927
The kid's here.

24:37.000 --> 24:39.287
I'm at fault here.

24:39.360 --> 24:41.488
You really are hopeless.

24:41.560 --> 24:44.530
I told you when we
were still at school.

24:44.600 --> 24:47.331
There's more to life
than getting rich.

24:47.400 --> 24:51.007
You want to be more
evil than Jiao Shengli?

24:51.080 --> 24:53.321
How can you compare me with him?

24:53.400 --> 24:55.562
If not him, then who?

24:55.680 --> 24:57.842
You and he were classmates.

24:57.920 --> 25:02.403
Look what he's made of
himself compared to us here.

25:03.080 --> 25:07.722
You have your own
place in Wujinshan.

25:07.800 --> 25:13.682
But my husband and I don't
even have a home of our own.

25:15.560 --> 25:17.005
Enough of this.

25:17.080 --> 25:20.448
If you have time on your hands,
why not open a restaurant?

25:20.520 --> 25:23.729
Or a shop? To earn
money and get married.

25:23.800 --> 25:28.124
Your life belongs to you.
Stop caring what others do.

25:31.880 --> 25:34.850
My dear, wait and see.

25:34.920 --> 25:39.482
I can be more evil than the
village chief or Jiao.

26:10.080 --> 26:12.003
Isn't that Mr. Golf?

26:14.480 --> 26:16.721
- What did you call me?
- Mr. Golf.

26:16.800 --> 26:20.247
Everyone calls you Mr. Golf now.
Didn't you know?

26:39.760 --> 26:41.364
Mr. Golf!

26:56.120 --> 26:57.645
I...

27:00.120 --> 27:01.451
Lin Chong...

27:05.000 --> 27:08.527
unsheathed my sword and, in anger,

27:08.600 --> 27:11.444
slew two of Gao Qiu's henchmen.

27:11.520 --> 27:14.000
Fortunately for me,

27:14.080 --> 27:16.651
Officer Chai gave me a document

27:16.720 --> 27:20.805
which enabled me to
come to Mount Liang.

29:30.000 --> 29:31.764
Good morning.

29:32.400 --> 29:33.686
Dahai, good morning.

29:33.760 --> 29:35.808
I want a word with your husband.

29:35.880 --> 29:37.723
Go ahead.

29:48.440 --> 29:50.010
Write.

29:53.640 --> 29:55.369
Write what?

29:58.040 --> 30:01.249
You know how much the
village chief embezzled.

30:01.360 --> 30:04.728
- Write a confession.
- You're being ridiculous.

30:13.400 --> 30:15.926
What are you doing?
That's dangerous.

30:17.000 --> 30:18.809
Write it down.

30:21.720 --> 30:23.404
Write!

30:34.040 --> 30:35.405
Write.

31:00.440 --> 31:01.805
Shoot.

31:04.120 --> 31:05.690
Shoot me here.

31:19.320 --> 31:22.244
You're too much of a
coward to kill me.

32:53.080 --> 32:56.209
Village Chief. It's Liuliu.

32:56.280 --> 32:58.248
I just started work.

32:59.720 --> 33:01.882
What do you want done?

33:04.080 --> 33:07.368
Okay, don't worry.
I'll do it this afternoon.

33:08.480 --> 33:10.244
Mr. Golf.

33:10.320 --> 33:12.482
- Where's the chief?
- At the temple.

33:15.520 --> 33:18.569
What did you just call me?

33:19.040 --> 33:20.326
Mr. Golf.

33:20.400 --> 33:23.085
Isn't that your foreign name?

33:23.160 --> 33:24.844
Little bastard.

33:24.920 --> 33:26.604
What did you say?

33:54.440 --> 33:56.329
- Dahai.
- Where are you off to?

33:56.400 --> 34:00.086
Fengjie. Going hunting?

34:00.160 --> 34:01.924
Hunting animals.

34:22.880 --> 34:24.962
Stop fooling around.

34:34.480 --> 34:36.322
Calm down.

34:37.560 --> 34:40.688
Let's sit down and talk.

34:41.159 --> 34:42.969
We can sort it out.

35:01.360 --> 35:04.762
Listen, don't be impulsive.

35:15.040 --> 35:16.530
Let's sit down.

36:01.400 --> 36:03.050
Bastard!

37:29.520 --> 37:31.284
Dahai?

37:44.960 --> 37:46.962
How can we fix this?

37:47.040 --> 37:48.246
Just tell me.

39:49.360 --> 39:50.805
Hey.

39:52.480 --> 39:54.767
You got a light?

39:54.840 --> 39:56.330
No.

40:12.160 --> 40:14.162
Motorcycle taxi.

40:28.000 --> 40:30.446
- Where to, buddy?
- The expressway.

40:30.520 --> 40:32.443
Let's go.

40:57.680 --> 41:02.402
Our Mrs. Zhou here worked
hard to raise her children.

41:02.520 --> 41:04.727
Now it's her 70th birthday,

41:04.800 --> 41:08.930
so let's wish her happiness,
good health and a long life.

41:11.200 --> 41:15.091
And now, let's welcome her
second son and his family,

41:15.200 --> 41:17.248
with their birthday greetings.

41:17.320 --> 41:19.322
San'er is here!

41:21.120 --> 41:23.361
The youngest son is back.

41:32.760 --> 41:33.841
You're back.

41:33.920 --> 41:35.922
Brother.

41:53.920 --> 41:56.526
Why are you running off?

41:56.600 --> 41:58.170
Come here.

42:04.160 --> 42:05.400
Mother.

42:21.000 --> 42:22.490
Don't cry.

43:08.920 --> 43:11.048
Where did you come from?

43:15.080 --> 43:17.367
I came by boat.

43:18.760 --> 43:20.489
And before that?

43:25.640 --> 43:27.449
I got your money transfers.

43:27.520 --> 43:29.568
130,000 yuan in all.

43:32.200 --> 43:34.009
That's right.

43:37.360 --> 43:41.251
The most recent one
came from Shanxi.

44:02.720 --> 44:06.520
I earned it in Wuhan and
sent it from Shanxi.

44:11.960 --> 44:13.849
I don't want your money.

44:38.760 --> 44:40.888
Your brothers are coming.

45:12.240 --> 45:16.245
Mother's birthday was on the 7th
day of the 11th lunar month.

45:16.320 --> 45:20.450
But we two had to work that day.
We couldn't get home.

45:20.520 --> 45:23.729
Our relatives couldn't
get here either.

45:24.480 --> 45:26.926
Since New Year is now and
many people come home,

45:27.000 --> 45:29.571
we decided to celebrate today.

45:32.520 --> 45:37.162
I'll go through it for you both.

45:37.680 --> 45:40.365
For Mother's 70th
birthday celebrations

45:40.440 --> 45:46.322
we received gifts of money
totaling 10,270 yuan.

45:47.840 --> 45:49.968
12 tables of guests.

45:50.040 --> 45:54.090
To buy meat, vegetables,
wine and cigarettes,

45:54.160 --> 45:59.007
the total cost was 6,477
yuan and 33 cents.

46:00.000 --> 46:03.083
I hired a host for 800 yuan.

46:03.160 --> 46:05.891
Taking all expenses into account,

46:05.960 --> 46:11.285
I had to spend 7,485
yuan and 42 cents.

46:11.360 --> 46:13.567
That was the total cost.

46:15.600 --> 46:20.003
What's left is 2,784
yuan and 58 cents.

46:21.200 --> 46:24.090
This money, the way I see it,

46:24.160 --> 46:27.289
should be shared between
us three and Mother.

46:27.360 --> 46:28.885
A quarter each.

46:28.960 --> 46:32.965
I've already divided it
into four equal shares.

46:33.720 --> 46:36.371
- Right, Second Brother?
- Yes.

46:37.720 --> 46:40.963
I don't need a share.
Give mine to Mother.

46:47.240 --> 46:51.882
I bought ten packs of cigarettes.
A good brand.

46:53.640 --> 46:55.768
There are nine left.

46:55.840 --> 46:59.242
So, that makes three each.

47:01.960 --> 47:06.841
As the oldest brother
I have to be impartial.

47:08.800 --> 47:11.963
If you want your share
to go to Mother,

47:12.480 --> 47:14.687
give it to her yourself.

47:49.120 --> 47:52.249
People usually worship
the gods tomorrow.

47:53.760 --> 47:56.127
I'm worshiping ghosts.

48:28.400 --> 48:31.643
The gods were to blame.

48:32.480 --> 48:35.802
If you have any grievances,
tell heaven about them.

49:37.600 --> 49:40.888
Is Qinqin in Dongguan?
Didn't she come back with you?

49:40.960 --> 49:43.440
She's gone to Zhongshan.

49:43.800 --> 49:44.961
She won't be back.

49:46.720 --> 49:49.121
She tested HIV positive.

49:49.720 --> 49:51.609
AIDS?

49:52.120 --> 49:54.646
Didn't she work in a factory?

49:55.320 --> 49:59.006
Impossible to make a decent living.

49:59.320 --> 50:03.644
Lili has a hair salon in Zhongshan,
so Qinqin went to work there.

50:04.600 --> 50:09.083
She provided "special services."
That's how she got AIDS.

50:09.600 --> 50:10.726
Bloody...

50:11.560 --> 50:13.324
you slept with her once.

50:13.400 --> 50:15.926
You'd better have a check-up.

50:16.480 --> 50:18.448
Don't talk crap.

50:18.520 --> 50:21.842
Get a check-up, quick.
Good luck with it.

50:21.920 --> 50:26.847
What's your wife up to in Tianjin
while you're stuck here?

50:26.960 --> 50:29.566
You should get her checked up.

50:29.640 --> 50:31.881
- Maybe you have HIV.
- What?

50:31.960 --> 50:34.088
You should keep your mouth shut.

50:34.160 --> 50:36.208
You want to die?

50:36.520 --> 50:39.171
Scumbag! Let's settle
this right now!

50:39.600 --> 50:42.331
Action? Let's see it, then.

50:42.400 --> 50:46.007
Only 78 minutes to go
till the New Year bell.

50:46.520 --> 50:49.490
Think you can take me?

52:24.200 --> 52:27.124
- Shall we set off a firework?
- Great!

52:32.960 --> 52:34.610
Watch.

53:06.160 --> 53:08.845
Tickets to Guangzhou, 240 yuan.

53:08.920 --> 53:12.003
Wuhan. Anybody for Wuhan?

53:16.680 --> 53:18.364
Want a ticket?

